423
00:26:47,702 --> 00:26:48,843
<i>Kau tak bingung?</i>

424
00:26:48,843 --> 00:26:50,202
<i>Kau harus sadar.</i>

425
00:26:51,212 --> 00:26:52,442
<i>Choi Soo Ji.</i>

426
00:26:52,972 --> 00:26:54,543
<i>Kau akan tetap di sana?</i>

427
00:26:54,682 --> 00:26:57,853
<i>Ayo turun, dan makanlah bersamaku.</i>

428
00:26:58,182 --> 00:27:00,452
<i>Aku bisa gila.</i>

429
00:27:00,452 --> 00:27:02,422
<i>Kenapa aku barusan
mendengar suaranya?</i>

430
00:27:02,982 --> 00:27:04,123
<i>Ini sangat menjengkelkan.</i>

